name: The Shire - Auenland
description: Nidderau is the place where I live and the area is called "Auenland" the shire. As in Lord of the Rings, it's a beautiful place, just without hobbits. A river takes it's way through the are and some times the year, the river floods all the grass. During blue hour and with a little fog, this beautiful area turns into a spooky, horror movie, scene.
